data.description: This home situated in a country setting offers tranquility from the hustle and bustle of city life. Inside this 4BR/4BA home You’ll find an array of upgrades. The Updated appliances, cabinets, countertops, backsplash add a touch of luxury while new windows flood each room with natural light. The heart of the home has an open floor plan, fireplace, kitchen island and new pellet stove adding character and functionality. The 3 bay workshop is perfect for DIY projects. Situated on 8.4-acres, this property offers plenty of room to roam. Convenient to both Albertville or Guntersville you can explore nature, visit local shops and restaurants, or commute to work, everything is within reach.
